creator: World Vision Development Foundation, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
The World Vision Philippines mobile app is for sponsors who have sponsored children under World Vision Philippines office.
This was designed as a gateway for our sponsors to easily connect with their sponsored child and their community.
Some of the special features include the option of sending a letter and even scheduling a visit with your sponsored child. You get to experience this convenience with just a few taps on your phone.
Other features include:
• Community updates
• Donation history
• Sending of Deposit slip
• World Vision updates
Get the World Vision Philippines app today, give your donation with just a few taps, and stay connected with us.
descriptionShort: Connect with your World Vision sponsored child with a click of a button!
